    specialty: 'Plastic Surgeon',
    surgeries: '50+ Endomidface',
    testimonial:
      'The learning curve was much faster than I expected. By the 15th case I already felt confident. Today, with over 50 procedures, Face Moderna® is my main rejuvenation technique.',
    image: '/images/testimonials/avatars/alumni-avatar-1.png',
    graduationYear: '2022',
    featured: true,
  },
  {
    name: 'Dr. Carolina S.',
    city: 'Rio de Janeiro, RJ',
    specialty: 'Plastic Surgeon',
    surgeries: '35+ Endomidface',
    testimonial:
      'The tactile feedback from direct vision completely changes the safety of the procedure. I can feel each anatomical plane and have millimeter control of repositioning.',
    image: '/images/testimonials/avatars/alumni-avatar-2.png',
    graduationYear: '2023',
    featured: true,
  },
  {
    name: 'Dr. Roberto F.',
    city: 'Belo Horizonte, MG',
    specialty: 'Plastic Surgeon',
